# Datasets and Simulation

**Task:** Discrete image classification only.

**Datasets:** CIFAR-10, CIFAR-100, MNIST, FMNIST, FEMNIST.

**Statistical heterogeneity:** Dirichlet ($\alpha$) partitioning only for non-IID client splits.

**System heterogeneity:** Per-client bandwidth from uniform draws (e.g. $U(5, 20)$ Mbps) to model stragglers.

Test $\alpha \in \{0.1, 1.0, 10.0\}$ from extreme skew to near-IID.
